---
title: Turkey and Black Bean Chili with Cheddar Cheese and Sour Cream
description: Nothing says autumn like a big bowl of warm chili! In this oh -so-quick and tasty version, chorizo is stewed with black beans. It wouldn't be chili without the fixin's, so we're topping it off with sour cream, cheddar cheese and spiced tortilla chips!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chili-au-chorizo-et-aux-haricots-noirs-96561cc6-35309ea7.jpg
